Client Usage
------------
login
    prompt for pass
    show virtual folder
    mask passwords
    highlight active lines
    shortcuts to copy line without showing

CLI Usage
---------
set-file {path-glob} -> json::list<matched paths>
get-file {path-glob} -> json::list<matched paths>

get {path} -> info
set {path} {text-content} -> status

list {path-glob} -> json::list<matched paths>
remove {path-glob} -> json::list<matched paths>

Backup Operations
-----------------
verify-crc {path-glob} -> status
update-crc {path-glob} -> status
pack -> json::status (append in a linear fashion, maybe)

